{"type":"message","id":"7add9363","parentId":"ee97e9e2","timestamp":"2026-03-09T16:40:03.203Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_38fe8b1a790648b193bd6cd8","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"## 实时数据获取操作\n\n**重要提示**\n- 以下描述的文件都在~/.openclaw/workspace-main-stock/stock路径下，\n  如'realtime-data.txt'实际路径为：~/.openclaw/workspace-main-stock/stock/realtime-data.txt\n\n### 操作流程\n\n1、如果realtime-data.txt里的内容不为空，则清空后进行下一步；否则直接进行下一步；\n2、使用tushare-data skill，获取数据判断今日是否收盘，未收盘，则进行下一步；否则，结束本次任务；\n3、使用tushare-data skill，按照get-data-template.md内的格式要求获取自选股的实时数据，保存在realtime-data.txt里；\n4、按照alert-rules.md中的预警规则和以下条件过滤获取到的实时数据：\n   - 3.1、满足预警规则中任意一条条件；\n   - 3.2、只返回满足预警规则的数据；\n5、如果存在满足条件的数据，则进行下一步；否则，结束本次任务。\n6、使用openclaw message send --channel feishu --account stock --message xxx 命令，将数据通过飞书(feishu)渠道推送给用户ID为：ou_9d907d39fb19b50579ba289b30041fc5的用户；\n7、推送的数据格式参考alert-template.md的内容要求。\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773074403201}}
{"type":"message","id":"b4a96f5a","parentId":"7add9363","timestamp":"2026-03-09T16:40:07.279Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I understand the task. I need to:\n1. Check and clear realtime-data.txt if not empty\n2. Use tushare-data skill to check if market is closed today\n3. If market is open, get real-time stock data according to get-data-template.md\n4. Filter data based on alert-rules.md\n5. If there's matching data, send via Feishu to the specified user using alert-template.md format\n\nLet me read the related configuration files to understand the requirements better.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_59e98d0854be4696bacf8959","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"~/.openclaw/workspace-main-stock/stock/get-data-template.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_e7a775b7cd6f47ccb5ca253a","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"~/.openclaw/workspace-main-stock/stock/alert-rules.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_064856e6ba7a44adb5cdd2e7","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"~/.openclaw/workspace-main-stock/stock/alert-template.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_e145522ae5154a27848f76c2","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"~/.openclaw/workspace-main-stock/stock/realtime-data.txt"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-397b-a17b","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773074403203}}
{"type":"message","id":"18054cbe","parentId":"b4a96f5a","timestamp":"2026-03-09T16:40:07.282Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_59e98d0854be4696bacf8959","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"## 数据获取模板\n\n按照以下格式获取【我的自选股票】的最新行情数据：\n\n【必选字段】\n1. 代码 (Stock Code) - 6 位数字/字母组合\n2. 名称 (Stock Name) - 中文全称\n3. 当前股价 (Current Price) - ¥XX.XX 元\n4. 涨跌幅 (Change %) - +X.XX% / -X.XX%\n5. 涨跌额(Price Change) - ¥XX.XX 元\n5. 时间点 (Timestamp) - YYYY-MM-DD HH:MM:SS\n\n【可选字段 - 根据需求添加】\n- 昨收价 (Previous Close)\n- 今开价 (Open Price)\n- 最高价 (High)\n- 最低价 (Low)\n- 成交量 (Volume)\n- 成交额 (Amount)\n- 市盈率 (PE Ratio)\n- 总市值 (Market Cap)\n- 涨跌额 (Price Change)\n- 换手率 (Turnover Rate)\n\n【数据源要求】\n- 优先级：Tushare Pro > 东方财富 > 同花顺\n- 实时性：优先使用盘口最新报价\n- 准确性：需交叉验证（建议用网页端确认）\n\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773074407280}}
{"type":"message","id":"855db15f","parentId":"18054cbe","timestamp":"2026-03-09T16:40:07.284Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_e7a775b7cd6f47ccb5ca253a","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"## 预警规则\n\n### 通用规则\n1、下跌 > 3% → 触发\n2、上涨 > 5% → 触发\n\n### 个股专属规则\n**中国石油 (601857.SH)**:\n- 🟢 涨幅 > 2% → 触发预警\n- 🔴 跌幅 > 1% → 触发预警\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773074407283}}
{"type":"message","id":"7550051f","parentId":"855db15f","timestamp":"2026-03-09T16:40:07.287Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_064856e6ba7a44adb5cdd2e7","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"## 预警数据输出模版\n\n【输出格式】\n表格形式，每页输出10条数据,按涨跌幅排序，高亮异常波动\n\n示例：\n| 代码 | 名称 | 当前价 | 涨跌幅 | 涨跌额| 时间 |\n|------|------|--------|--------|-------|------|\n| XXXX | XXXX | ¥XX.XX | +X.XX% |￥XXXX |12:00 |\n\n⚙️ 预警规则\n• 📉 下跌 > x% → 触发\n• 📈 上涨 > x% → 触发\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773074407285}}
